Class SimpleDBTest

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.cs.cs4432.project1.team10.SimpleDBTest

public class SimpleDBTest
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements the methods called in SimpleDBTestHarness. Each method prepares an SQL statement, sends it via a JDBC driver to be processed by SimpleDB, and finally parses the results (if necessary).

Author:
Eric Greer, Matt Runkle, Andrew Yee
